<br />
<strong><a href="/scp-cn-453">SCP-CN-453</a></strong> <strong>by</strong> <strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dongdong37" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3514258); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3514258&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610160640" alt="dongdong37" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3514258)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dongdong37" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3514258); return false;">dongdong37</a></span></strong><br />
<br />
