</div>
</div>
<br />
<br />
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/touch">吟游诗人的笔录：羊皮卷</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354275&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="OlivaFute" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354275)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;">OlivaFute</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>世界仍未开始，此为序章。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/fallen-world">陨落的世界</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/astra-glorice-sws" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3363881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3363881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="Astra_Glorice_SWS" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3363881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/astra-glorice-sws" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3363881); return false;">Astra_Glorice_SWS</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>陨落的永远是世界，堕落的永远是人心。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/shamodercjl">沙漠的日常记录</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/knight-li-zx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3267343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3267343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="Knight Li ZX" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3267343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/knight-li-zx" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3267343); return false;">Knight Li ZX</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>命不久矣。我不想死。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/jijinhuidelinian">基金会的理念</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3457409&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="Adeptus Custodes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3457409)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;">Adeptus Custodes</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>我哑口无言，难道基金会崇高的工作就这么被否定了？控制收容保护真的只是我们一厢情愿？</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/the-beloved-is-gone">所爱之人已逝</a>By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354275&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="OlivaFute" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354275)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;">OlivaFute</a></span>&amp;<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/astra-glorice-sws" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3363881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3363881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="Astra_Glorice_SWS" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3363881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/astra-glorice-sws" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3363881); return false;">Astra_Glorice_SWS</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>爱自于他心，不可辨之虚实，人往心犹故。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/catdanger">吟游诗人的笔录：危机猫</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/saopig" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3715193); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3715193&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="saopig" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3715193)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/saopig" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3715193); return false;">saopig</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>简约的黑白配色的餐厅里，伫立着一只橘猫，死死盯着Oliva。橘猫回头了。弋尘躲闪不及。四目相交。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/laoyan">老研</a><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;&#32;</span>By<span style="color: #0000cd">Lee Knight</span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>至于老研自己的人事，反正大家都认识他重新录入也是方便。而老研每次录入的人事记录都是一模一样。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/noology">Dr.Oliva的讲座抄录：关于精神</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354275&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="OlivaFute" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354275)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;">OlivaFute</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>抄录字迹过模糊，无法辨认</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/you-and-she">你和她</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3457409&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="Adeptus Custodes" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3457409)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adeptus-custodes" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3457409); return false;">Adeptus Custodes</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>让我掉下眼泪的，不止，昨夜的酒。</em></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>让我依依不舍的，只有，你的温柔。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/the-night-watchman">吟游诗人的笔录：守夜人与海</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3354275&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="OlivaFute" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3354275)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/olivafute" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3354275); return false;">OlivaFute</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>日出东方，海尽嫣红。</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><a href="/the-missing-lancer">骑士不在的周一</a> By <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-lancelot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3494246); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3494246&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609639258" alt="A Lancelot" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3494246)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-lancelot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3494246); return false;">A Lancelot</a></span><br /></p>
</div>
<blockquote>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family:华文楷体;font-size: 100%"><em>Lancelot失踪了吗？你呢？</em></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p><br />
<br /></p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
